477
00:20:05,499 --> 00:20:08,252
[whoosh]

478
00:20:13,215 --> 00:20:15,259
[whispered murmuring]

479
00:20:15,259 --> 00:20:18,304
[siren wailing]

480
00:20:20,306 --> 00:20:22,808
- Bishop Six,
we got a hit on Killgrave.

481
00:20:22,808 --> 00:20:25,144
25 Beacon Court.
