484
00:20:29,774 --> 00:20:32,777
[suspenseful music]

485
00:20:32,777 --> 00:20:35,780
[device continues beeping]

486
00:20:35,780 --> 00:20:42,828
♪ ♪

487
00:20:47,333 --> 00:20:50,795
